data.description: This splendid home harmoniously blends modern elegance with timeless charm. Boasting four bedrooms and a versatile loft, it caters to diverse lifestyles. The updated kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring granite countertops and state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances. Two and a half bathrooms exude spa-like luxury with contemporary finishes. Updated lighting fixtures grace each room, casting a warm glow throughout. The 12 x 24 all-season room, bathed in natural light, and additional luxury covered porch serves as a tranquil retreat. An extended parking pad perfect for RV or Boat. Above ground pool with deck for summer entertaining. This residence offers refined living with carefully curated features, transcending the ordinary to provide a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication.
